high_descs: Go to the sidetable just below the window.
Open the microwave. Place the apple inside the microwave on the left side. Close the microwave. Turn on the microwave light. Turn it off. Open the door. Take the apple from the microwave.
Move to the left of the countertop.
Place the apple on the left side of the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Find an apple, microwave it and place it on the left side of the countertop.

high_descs: Turn around and walk straight to the living room side table.
Take the apple from the side table.
Turn around and turn left and walk straight to the microwave.
Place the apple on the microwave.
Take the apple from the microwave and turn around to the counter top.
Place the apple on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Place the apple on the counter top.

high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the side table
Pick up apple from the side table
Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the microwave
Place apple inside the microwave and then take it out
Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the counter top
Place apple on the counter top
anns.task_desc: Heating apple on microwave and placing it in counter top
